{"tid":1725444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據報休班警柴灣遇襲　擎槍示警跌子彈","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T18:04:09.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"577f24b119576a88afe84ace1eeb15d2ea97069b","tid":1725444,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bullet_NxGs1_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbullet_NxGs1_1200x0.JPG&h=f6ce847a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有傳媒引述消息報道，有休班警員在柴灣遇襲，曾擎槍示警，跌出一粒子彈。《立場新聞》凌晨 1 時許向警察公共關係科查詢，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n《東方日報》引述消息報道，有約30人男子在近樂軒臺對開，包圍一名休班警員毆打，期間另一名休班警員曾用警棍嘗試制止，曾擎槍示警，期間相信跌出一粒子彈及遺失一枝警棍。報道指兩名警員均受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n無線新聞則引述消息報道，該名休班警員跑步經過柴灣街市時遇襲，曾擎槍示警，跌出一粒子彈。網上流傳相信是警員跌出一粒子彈的相片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%93%8E%E6%A7%8D%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E8%B7%8C%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E6%2593%258E%25E6%25A7%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=9b6ebad0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E6%2593%258E%25E6%25A7%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&h=f9e8a8c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%93%8E%E6%A7%8D%E7%A4%BA%E8%A